accessrestrict.head: Access Restrictions
accessrestrict.p: Restricted documents have been sealed within the collection.

prefercite.p: Records of the Virginia Secretary of the Commonwealth, 2010-2013. Accession 51157, State government records collection, The Library of Virginia, Richmond, Va. 23219.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: Transferred from the Virginia Secretary of Administration on January 23, 2014.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content
scopecontent.p: Secretary of the Commonwealth records, 2010-2013, consist of xx archival boxes and are divided into x series. Series have been designated for These records document the work of the Secretary of the Commonwealth during the McDonnell administration and were created or collected, 2010-2013, though some documents in this collection pre-date this time period.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: This collection is arranged into the following series:

scopecontent.p: This series is housed in 4 boxes and is arranged chronologically. The majority of the correspondence is comprised of correspondence received by the Secretary of the Commonwealth.
Invitations, 2010-2014, are housed in 3 boxes and are arranged chronologically.

did.unittitle: Series III. Executive orders and directives, 2010-2013.

scopecontent.p: Executive orders and directives, 2010-2013, are housed in 1 box and are arranged by order or directive number.
Proclamations, 2010-2013, are housed in 1 box and are arranged chronologically. There are only five proclamations in this series.

did.unittitle: Rescue Squad and Emergency Medical Services Week, 2010 May 16-22.
Series V. Special project and subject files, 2010-2013.

scopecontent.p: Special event and subject files, 2010-2013, are housed in 3 boxes and are arranged alphabetically.
